
<!-- 
Description
- Create a password input that shows real-time feedback on password strength. Display requirements checklist and strength meter.

What You'll Learn
- Regular expressions (regex)
- Real-time input validation
- Visual feedback
- Multiple condition checking

------ Step-by-Step Approach ------
1. Create input field and feedback area
2. Define password requirements
3. Check each requirement on input
4. Update visual feedback (checklist, meter)
5. Calculate overall strength score 
-->


